1986;;Foreign Body;;British;;Ronald Neame;;Warren Mitchell, Victor Banerjee, Amanda Donohoe;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foreign_Body_(film);;Banerjee stars as Ram Das, a jobless Indian man who, tired of life in Calcutta, steals money from his father in order to afford a passage to Britain and while there, falls in love with a white woman.[1]